  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206450/extras/a3480efe74f3ff69730baf2d3cce50ee.poster.avif?t=1760249588\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206450/extras/a3480efe74f3ff69730baf2d3cce50ee.webm?t=1760249588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206450/extras/a3480efe74f3ff69730baf2d3cce50ee.mp4?t=1760249588\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Dwarfer is a logic-based 2D puzzle game where you control a squad of two dwarves navigating through treacherous caves in search of gold. Each step taken by one dwarf mirrors the movement of the other, making timing and planning crucial to success. The caves are filled with spikes, skeletons, and other traps, forcing you to think several moves ahead to ensure both dwarves escape unharmed.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206450/extras/3f7ec25f725345352041de4ed85c8f3b.poster.avif?t=1760249588\" width=600 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206450/extras/3f7ec25f725345352041de4ed85c8f3b.webm?t=1760249588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206450/extras/3f7ec25f725345352041de4ed85c8f3b.mp4?t=1760249588\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Key Features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Synchronized movement of two characters, adding depth to the puzzle mechanics.<br></li><li>Numerous levels with increasing difficulty and new challenges.<br></li><li>A variety of deadly traps and enemies to outwit.<br></li><li>Unique gameplay requiring strategic thinking and foresight.<br></li><li>Challenging puzzles with consequences for every move.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206450/extras/63dfbffc526e987e66c4a31edad400e6.avif?t=1760249588\" width=600 height=200 /></span>",
