nd foresight.<br></li><li>Challenging puzzles with consequences for every move.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206450/extras/63dfbffc526e987e66c4a31edad400e6.avif?t=1760249588\" width=600 height=200 /></span>",
